    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bridges having only one span, being anchored only at each end with no supports in the middle; the longest single span bridges are suspension bridges. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
